Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, what'll happen to the Galactic Alliance once you defeat all the Hideauze?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber, search for a job I can do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Search complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No results.{depressing}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My database is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no data regarding\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}Gargantia's labor market.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a job for you,\Nthere's gotta be one for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your comparison with\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}me is not applicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have close to no aptitude for non-combat tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend maintaining\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the best option\N for me is to stand by?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree that it is morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you working\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you building?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of a hull-connecting machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure rely on you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're still working on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bevel told me it's a flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with sound, it is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You're working\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}so hard to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is useless. Meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for loading the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}freight the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is there no money in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Galactic Alliance does not allow soldiers\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to own private goods during their service.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very motivating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy, I want to work by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, that sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What work is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a delivery girl, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a drag if everyone had to walk around\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to hand over letters and packages themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I deliver stuff for them, \Nand in exchange, I get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we support each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Support each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I would support someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So first, you should think\N about what {\i1}you{\i0} wanna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not an easy question...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not familiar with\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}how we live, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do? Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
