Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Sign here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,90,,How's work? Do you have enough people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,90,,This guy here's looking for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,90,,Ah, you're that boy from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,90,,Ain't that something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,90,,One of my men retired last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,90,,Oh, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.69,Default,,0,0,90,,But I already got someone to replace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:10.19,Default,,0,0,90,,Don't worry about it! There's always fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been like this ever since\N we missed the last riptide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know if\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}things get busy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we're busy trying\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to organize all of these invoices.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something we\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}can let a newbie handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about treasure hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We found a nice target,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but it'll take three more\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}days until we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta do my deliveries soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try searching alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! A bit higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass! I told you to go higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Left here! {\i1}Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought the requirements\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}for work would be so strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber, how's your database update coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still no jobs\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}that match your skill set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The fleet's engines are stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha sulking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion, the fleet stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get together! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out this huge chunk of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna fill us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you got\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}your hands on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you really\N afford to throw a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages since our last calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a bunch of stuff\N that needs repairing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get to where I'm at, \Nyour employees do all the work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start with Flange's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the power been shut down yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this way for the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that was {\i1}your{\i0} job \Nthey were talking about, Pinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, on days of calm, when the wind dies off and the sea quiets down,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we do maintenance on the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We get out of the galaxy current and cut the electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so all that's left to do is repair work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We all get a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Bevel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, this is what the sea's like \Nwhen there's no wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya! Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
