Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, doesn't that look nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll feel good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get rid of these lame clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real scorcher today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ordum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy getting this meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, still no power?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about putting that\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}metalhead over there to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You need them fried?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\an7\fscx33\fscy23\pos(640,660)}m 276 20 l 264 20 l 264 -120 l 288 -120 l 288 20 l 276 20 m 288 20 l 312 20 l 312 -120 l 288 -120 l 288 -180 l 264 -180 l 264 -60 l 240 -60 l 240 20 l 264 20 l 264 80 l 288 80 l 288 20 m 368 20 l 356 20 l 356 -120 l 380 -120 l 380 20 l 368 20 m 380 20 l 404 20 l 404 -120 l 380 -120 l 380 -180 l 356 -180 l 356 -120 l 332 -120 l 332 -60 l 356 -60 l 356 80 l 380 80 l 380 20 m -92 20 l -104 20 l -104 -120 l -80 -120 l -80 20 l -92 20 m -80 20 l -56 20 l -56 -120 l -80 -120 l -80 -180 l -104 -180 l -104 -76 l -128 -76 l -128 20 l -104 20 l -104 80 l -80 80 l -80 20 m -12 80 l -12 80 l -12 -120 l 12 -120 l 12 20 l 12 20 m 12 20 l 36 20 l 36 -120 l 12 -120 l 12 -180 l -12 -180 l -12 -120 l -36 -120 l -36 80 l -12 80 l -12 80 l -12 80 l 12 20 m -184 20 l -196 20 l -196 -120 l -172 -120 l -172 20 l -184 20 m -172 20 l -148 20 l -149 -8 l -172 -8 l -172 -180 l -196 -180 l -196 -120 l -220 -120 l -220 20 l -196 20 l -196 80 l -172 80 l -172 20 m -368 20 l -380 20 l -380 -120 l -356 -120 l -356 20 l -368 20 m -356 20 l -332 20 l -332 -92 l -356 -92 l -356 -180 l -380 -180 l -380 -120 l -404 -120 l -404 20 l -380 20 l -380 80 l -356 80 l -356 20 m -276 20 l -288 20 l -288 -120 l -264 -120 l -264 20 l -276 20 m -264 -50 l -240 -50 l -240 -120 l -264 -120 l -264 -180 l -288 -180 l -288 -120 l -312 -120 l -312 20 l -288 20 l -288 80 l -264 80 l -264 20 m 92 20 l 80 20 l 80 -120 l 104 -120 l 104 20 l 92 20 m 104 20 l 128 20 l 128 -120 l 104 -120 l 104 -180 l 80 -180 l 80 -120 l 56 -120 l 56 -90 l 80 -90 l 80 80 l 104 80 l 104 20 m 184 20 l 172 20 l 172 -120 l 196 -120 l 196 20 l 184 20 m 196 -36 l 220 -36 l 220 -120 l 196 -120 l 196 -180 l 172 -180 l 172 -120 l 148 -120 l 148 20 l 172 20 l 172 80 l 196 80 l 196 20
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Target incinerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgot what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to that smelter granny's place and fetch me some stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fitting job for you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a job only you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're seriously\N sending Ledo {\i1}there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! He wasted all that meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on ya.
Comment: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{HALFTIME}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do my back next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ledo'll be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey, that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,90,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:57.73,Default,,0,0,90,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,90,,I'll probably get even fatter \N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}if I have some of that barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,90,,Even fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,90,,You of all people shouldn't have to worry about that, Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,90,,Everyone has their own standards. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,90,,I don't care about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,90,,Lots of guys like girls\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}with rounder figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.22,Default,,0,0,90,,Aren't we naïve?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,90,,Keep believing that, and\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}you're bound to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should start exercising...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ridget. Amy, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about the \Ncrane tower's sprinklers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The power's back up,\N but they won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you get up there with your surfkite to start the pump?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're about to\N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}have a barbecue party—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, whatever! I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbecue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for a race!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I don't need to\N worry about getting fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If they are so enthusiastic about eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,why do they worry so much \Nabout maintaining their figures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how girls think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprises there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, metalhead. You sure are black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the right place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hello there, lonely boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is {\i1}so{\i0} sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And such a juicy body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The finish line's the top\N of the crane tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch your takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I question the necessity of this action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you gonna\N fix my ship's winch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to it eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this when you're\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}supposed to be the busiest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying about the little details!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should join us for some meat! \NWe're about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna work at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The lieutenant is in\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}a state of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He can learn something about society.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the diving suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was overseeing the inspection \N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}and repair work of the ship's bilge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, when's the power coming back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The repairs are taking longer than expected, so probably not before sunset.{Btw, yes, this comma seems wrong. But I'd venture to say that the second phrase is actually a fragment with an implicit subject/verb of "the power will be back on." Hence, comma.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't started yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... your swimsuit's...\N pretty revealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Newcomers don't need\N to work night shifts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll become our number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your butt is simply {\i1}perfect{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So fresh! So much stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, why is it {\i1}always{\i0} Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But the race is still on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{sore!}{Hup!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing there anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I... do not really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it must've been rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to get back to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right down this street!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that was some good exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can eat as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I question the necessity of this action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat: I question the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}necessity of this action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I told ya, no moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Young'un, what do you\N intend to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If it'll settle things, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these parts for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to go back the way I came?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Who told everyone\N about the barbecue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, space boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta have something\N better than salt for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Who wants some?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, that granny's\N sauce really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get some\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}before it's all gone, Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, taste the\N fruit of your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You got enough to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried, since\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}you got back late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It was supposed to\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}be a party for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You didn't know?
